    <vamendmenttexta />

      <p>Point 2 remains as before; that is, it will still read:</p>
      <h4>5.2. Appointment</h4>
      <ol>
        <li>The Project Leader is elected by the Developers.</li>
        <li>The election begins nine weeks before the leadershippost
            becomes vacant, or (if it is too late already)
            immediately. </li>
        <li> ... </li>
      </ol>

      <p>
        <em>Rationale</em>: Having a buffer zone of three weeks is
        useful for continuity and/or cases where the nomination period
        must be extended.  A buffer zone has been included in DPL
        elections in recent years.

      </p>

